				</dl>
			</div>
			<div class="postright">
				<h3>bep 27: private torrents</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>I believe Azureus introduced private torrents, though please correct me on this.&nbsp; I would welcome someone on the Azureus team or who was involved in the creation of private torrents to please take over authorship of this BEP.<br /><br />This BEP simply codefies what is in many clients already and is previously described here<br /><br /><a href="http://www.azureuswiki.com/index.php/SecureTorrents" rel="nofollow">http://www.azureuswiki.com/index.php/SecureTorrents</a><br /><br />This BEP only addresses the &quot;private:1&quot; flag in the .torrent and not how private torrents are implemented in general, nor is the purpose of this BEP to discuss share ratios or other incentive mechanisms introduced by many private trackers.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="clearer"></div>
